AGI - A pilot died and another was injured after two ultralight aircraft crashed during a demonstration at the Beja Air Show in southern Portugal. The military air force reported that the victim is a Spanish citizen. The incident involved six planes that belonged to an acrobatic group of Spanish and Portuguese pilots called "Yak Stars". >
