A 169 million penthouse was sold at 105 million. Of eighteen real estate units, fourteen recorded a vertical cut of the price. The downturn is around 13 percent, but there is also more than 30 percent in a city where house prices increased by 11.3 percent. If someone was interested, you can search for information on the internet. The prices, we say, are downhill but not really accessible.
